{
 "name": "RPlog_Friendship_Shaken",
 "title": "Friendship Shaken",
 "summary": "In an Imperial detention block, Marshal Krieg summons the stormtrooper TK-4461 (Ansforth) and assigns him as interrogation muscle before visiting the captive Shael, a former friend he once knew. Offering food and bacta at a price, Krieg plays the role of reluctant benefactor while Ansforth brutally beats Shael, breaking her wrist, until she gives up the names Vengan and Draelis. Krieg orders the trooper out, tends Shael's injuries, and sedates her, masking his inner conflict behind a neutral Imperial facade. Shael, numb and broken, accepts treatment she cannot refuse and is left alone to await the next interrogator. The scene captures the cost of Krieg's divided loyalties and the erosion of an old friendship under Imperial duress.",
